了在动视和索尼之间的现有协议结束后，让《使命召唤》在 PlayStation 上保留三年时间的提案。 《使命召唤》在 PlayStation 上存在了近 20 年，他们的提案在很多层面上都是不足够的，没有考虑到对我们玩家的影响。我们希望保证 PlayStation 玩家继续拥有高质量的《使命召唤》体验，而微软的天破坏了这一原则。”索尼指责微软误导消费者：《使命召唤》只能在PS上保留3年"},"attached_info":"Cj4IwLrCqo7W7Y8TEAMaCDg1MDM5MTM0IM3G5ZgGMAI4R0Aecgk1NTI0MDE1MTB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"22 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6d9f7c8a9e0d3afd59e0756f55cc1f96.jpg?source=2044ae36"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"31_1662737227.0162077","card_id":"Q_20441865","target":{"id":20441865,"title":"在你的工作中设计PPT经常会用到哪些技巧？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/20441865","type":"question","created":1345864298,"answer_count":22,"follower_count":193,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[99,445,1115,2566,47782],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"你的页面都是用插入图片和直接打字构成的吗？这样做是不是浪费PPT的原有功能了？只需要插入图片和输入文字两个功能，PPT也太简单了，这样学PPT的做法对吗？"},"attached_info":"CjwIwLrCqo7W7Y8TEAMaBjM1NzE0OSDqhOGBBTAAOMEBQB9yCDIwNDQxODY1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"22 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d4025666efa6726a1130980fa90d1dff_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"32_1662737227.0173254","card_id":"Q_27493229","target":{"id":27493229,"title":"怎样成为一个高情商的人？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/27493229","type":"question","created":1420791972,"answer_count":424,"follower_count":12700,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1740,2566,4467,16178],"comment_count":14,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"最好有超级权威的参考资料啦！让大伙都增长一下知识"},"attached_info":"Cj0IwLrCqo7W7Y8TEAMaBzMxODAwODggpKG+pQUwDjicY0AgcggyNzQ5MzIyOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJ